APP ，这里的卡并非是网络原因，第一次见到网盘只提供全部暂停不提供全部下载，而每点击一次开始下载要等待 2-3 秒，假设有 60 项下载项被暂停了，以人类手指多线程速度重新恢复它们需要至少 1 分钟。<br />类似这样的体验只是冰山一角，百度网盘到处充斥着反人类的设计，加上开屏必须等待 5 秒空白启动页+5 秒开屏广告，不管你干啥去了回到百度网盘首先就要蒸发 5-10 秒，是我人生中遇到过最垃圾的 APP ，这辈子不会安装第二次。", "last_modified": 1759656381, "replies": 43, "id": 1163401}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_large.png?m=1524891806", "name": "google", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_normal.png?m=1524891806", "title": "Google", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/google", "topics": 3392, "footer": "", "header": "Google’s mission is to organize the world’s information and make it universally accessible and useful.", "title_alternative": "Google", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_mini.png?m=1524891806", "stars": 3780, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 65, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 474336, "username": "zehua", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/zehua", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d2eb/5e8d/474336_mini.png?m=1644295873", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d2eb/5e8d/474336_normal.png?m=1644295873", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d2eb/5e8d/474336_large.png?m=1644295873", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d2eb/5e8d/474336_xlarge.png?m=1644295873", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d2eb/5e8d/474336_xxlarge.png?m=1644295873", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d2eb/5e8d/474336_xxxlarge.png?m=1644295873", "created": 1583393417, "last_modified": 1644295873, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Danmen123", "last_touched": 1759666386, "title": "谷歌账户一直用不了 Gemini，每次都提示所在地区不支持", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1163408", "created": 1759645342, "deleted": 0, "content": "已经修改过了 profile 里面的地址了，更换了美国和日本的 ip 都不行，有没有人遇到过这个问题，难道只有我没法用 Gemini 吗？😭", "content_rendered": "已经修改过了 profile 里面的地址了，更换了美国和日本的 ip 都不行，